Sorry I didn't post for the last two days, guys, but I couldn't get 
online due to the New Year.

Oh, and HAPPY NEW YEAR!



::Prowl/FZ/Perndabot/Grimmler/Firearm::

Prowl rolls out of the way of one of FZ's missiles, turning in time 
to get out of the energy field as the missile detonates in the air. 
He turns around, diving down straight for FZ.

Before FZ can react, Prowl smashes into him, sending both bots flying 
downward.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Grimmler jumps back up, seeing Scattershot clenching his mouth shut 
and firing two missiles at the bot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Perndabot smashes into the ground but jumps up in a second, seeing 
Liono Prime's group fly into the battle. He growls. He still 
recognized the old Maximal commander.

Perndabot runs at Liono, firing two missiles from each missile 
launcher.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm fires off more charges at Double Punch.
